      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "2 Samuel 1:12",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "). Such national fasts are called by the rabbis \"fasts of the congregation,\" and were enjoined in times of great affliction.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "On the offerings, see Lev. i., 3.",
